{"tid":1751761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輸緊呀，贏左乜？","createTime":"2019-11-24T18:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:55:41.000Z","uid":221237,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"922bbe89a203dfecc454f37371eda5b395956324","tid":1751761,"uid":221237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"五千位亂世兒女等緊俾狗告<br />\n過萬手足抗爭受傷流血<br />\n爆頭爆眼斷手用拐杖<br />\n日日有人被自殺死因無可疑<br />\n呢次區選係真香港人向港共發出最後和解機會<br />\n立即成立獨立調查警暴委員會<br />\n<br />\n今次當選既民主派人士唔係你個人任何能力<br />\n係抗爭者既人血換黎架<br />\n記住要做好地區工作,服務街坊"},{"pid":"02b0b6c5ef1fbc0117a9e9a88a0a7dee3320a3a0","tid":1751761,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:05:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"53ff405754ccef9e21e8a5e83a3e02de3e7e6991","tid":1751761,"uid":221237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"想講下今日遊走幾個票站見聞<br />\n見到好多排隊都係中年以上，師奶<br />\n而家見到票數，應係好多都係同路人<br />\n希望大家尊重，唔好再叫廢老"},{"pid":"2255c48f4a2a8022ee6e0a5168f29be74b2cf882","tid":1751761,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:10:31.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"a4370bb71eed567de4af23814409d46bda5bfb6d","tid":1751